name: Lousy NFT-Shirt
description: Hello, friends. It would appear as though light has prevailed, and I have been unbanned from hic et nunc. Please let me take the opportunity to thank this wonderful community, for whom I am eternally grateful. My return to this magnificent virtual space of ours was achieved through the tireless efforts of countless individuals working around the clock to uncover the truth. We are all in this together. Thank you for believing in me, and our shared vision for the future. No refunds on the shirts. Policy.
